ge;\">警畜互助社持有大量物業可釘契</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20191217/2Z5CDIRXGB3SDL2DLXZJJ7MDNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191217%2F2Z5CDIRXGB3SDL2DLXZJJ7MDNM%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=bc5ac865\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191217%2F2Z5CDIRXGB3SDL2DLXZJJ7MDNM%2F&h=72433309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20191217/2Z5CDIRXGB3SDL2DLXZJJ7MDNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n【更新：警察「遮仔會」買賣物業紀錄】<br />\n[新地(016)於葵涌的九龍貿易中心(KCC)，由香港警察儲蓄互助社（HONG KONG POLICE CREDIT UNION）持有的B座四層半樓面<br />\n<br />\n最初警察「遮仔會」物業買賣的規模多屬「小打小鬧」性質，如九十年代購入的太子永光花園及尖沙嘴新文華中心成交價865萬及874萬元，最終持貨十餘年後分別以833萬及823萬元蝕讓。<br />\n<br />\n轉捩點在2005年，警察「遮仔會」以3,048萬元買入旺角華僑商業大廈舖位，至今年初以6,761萬元售出，帳面獲利達1.2倍或3,713萬元。<br />\n有承造按揭。]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該"},{"pid":"058c8d4df71f014b91b26e6c43d9dcd0573a8c76","tid":2054430,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5fe38bbf1611977f5402d741501845f274bf7558","tid":2054430,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27d48699f533c4b5c3e21867a228ba3d64a4af3","tid":2054430,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bf5e046cb7fda2b1beb0bb168707f15a27cc08","tid":2054430,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:47:11.000Z","msg":"推上去<br />\n等班港狗d錢攞唔返<img src=\"/assets/